Package jopt.js.api.exception

This package contains all exceptions specific to the JobScheduler project.

See:
          Description

Exception Summary
JobSchedulerRuntimeException A class to report any errors that are JobScheduler specific, but cannot be specified as a standard PropagationFailureException.
